<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to your Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/themes.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
</head>
<body class="<%= user.preferences.theme === 'dark' ? 'dark-theme' : '' %>">

    <%- include('partials/header', { user: user }) %>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="welcome-header">
            <h1>Welcome to Billboard, <%= user.name || user.displayName %>!</h1>
            <p>Your new space to capture ideas. Here are a few things you can do to get started.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fab fa-markdown"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Write with Markdown</h3>
                <p>Format your notes with headings, lists, bold, italics, and more using simple Markdown syntax.</p>
                <pre><code># My Title\n**Bold text**\n- A list item</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-hand-paper"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Organize Visually</h3>
                <p>Arrange your notes freely on the billboard. Drag and drop them to create the layout that works for you. The position is saved automatically.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Make It Yours</h3>
                <p>Visit the settings page to change your note colors, and switch between the light and dark themes to match your preference.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="main-cta-container">
            <a href="/index" class="btn btn-primary btn-launch">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Let's Get Started!
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/javascript/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>